=== test.112: force HT clock via CC.clk_ctl_st (Phase 6 kickoff) --- stage=0 ===
Date: Fri 17 Apr 18:58:39 BST 2026

Stage 0: test.112 — write CCS_FORCEHT (bit 1) to ChipCommon.clk_ctl_st, poll CCS_BP_ON_HT (bit 19) up to 10ms, log pmustatus/res_state. Tests whether simple force-HT brings up BBPLL without extra PMU config. skip_arm=1 keeps it isolated.

